               <p>JOHN HAZARD. I was near <placeName id="t18250630-22-crimeloc110">the Angel Inn, Islington</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18250630-22-crimeloc110" type="placeName" value="the Angel Inn, Islington"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18250630-22-crimeloc110" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250630-22-off108 t18250630-22-crimeloc110"></join>, on the 23d of June - a gentleman told me something; I turned round, and missed my handkerchief. I saw the prisoner and another person near me - they began running; I pursued, and called Stop thief! I went up to the prisoner, and took the handkerchief from him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18250630-22-person191">
