            . I heard the cry of Stop thief! I followed the prisoner, and took him with the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I saw the handkerchief laying on the pavement, took it up, and was walking along, when I was stopped.</p>
